Package main.java.ui

This package is responsible for creating and maintaining this User Interface.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Answer
    The Answer Class represents an Answer in the Sudoku game.
    Board
    Board is the class responsible for rendering the actual Sudoku Board.
    ButtonMenu
    ButtonMenu is a class that defines the left side of the Sudoku Board game.
    Chat  
    Chatter  
    GameUI
    GameUI is a BorderPane that handles all the UI elements.
    InfoMenu
    This class is responsible for creating and maintaining the ToolBar that holds player names.
    Notes
    This class represents the Notes that the user can make inside a single Square.
    Square
    This class represents a single square on the Sudoku Board.
